doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Blog Home - Start Bootstrap Template

        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body

        // Responsive navbar
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark
            .container
                a.navbar-brand(href='#!') Start Bootstrap
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#') Home
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#!') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#!') Contact
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.active(aria-current='page', href='#') Blog

        // Page header with logo and tagline
        header.py-5.bg-light.border-bottom.mb-4
            .container
                .text-center.my-5
                    h1.fw-bolder Welcome to Blog Home!
                    p.lead.mb-0 A Bootstrap 5 starter layout for your next blog homepage

        // Page content
        .container
            .row

                // Blog entries
                .col-lg-8

                    // Featured blog post
                    .card.mb-4
                        a(href='#!')
                            img.card-img-top(src='https://dummyimage.com/850x350/dee2e6/6c757d.jpg', alt='...')
                        .card-body
                            .small.text-muted January 1, 2023
                            h2.card-title Featured Post Title
                            p.card-text
                                | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Reiciendis aliquid atque, nulla? Quos cum ex quis soluta, a laboriosam. Dicta expedita corporis animi vero voluptate voluptatibus possimus, veniam magni quis!
                            a.btn.btn-primary(href='#!') Read more →

                    // Nested row for non-featured blog posts
                    .row

                        .col-lg-6
                            // Blog post
                            .card.mb-4
                                a(href='#!')
                                    img.card-img-top(src='https://dummyimage.com/700x350/dee2e6/6c757d.jpg', alt='...')
                                .card-body
                                    .small.text-muted January 1, 2023
                                    h2.card-title.h4 Post Title
                                    p.card-text
                                        | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Reiciendis aliquid atque, nulla.
                                    a.btn.btn-primary(href='#!') Read more →
